name: GotM November 2021 - Win/Win
description:
Win/Win is a vertical space shooter where killing each enemy slowly corrupts the game. Try to aim for the highest score without missing a single enemy. This game is inspired by Lose/Lose by Zach Gage, where killing an enemy would delete a random file from your computer.

WARNING: THIS GAME CONTAINS FLASHING IMAGES.
PLEASE DO NOT PLAY IF YOU HAVE A HISTORY OF EPILEPSY.

ENEMIES
• Green enemies will corrupt the game's sprites/visuals
• Blue enemies will corrupt the game's audio/music
• Red enemies will corrupt random memory addresses and game variables.

CONTROLS
Arrow Keys / D-Pad - Move left/right
Z / O - Fire

Also made available on Newgrounds and Itch.io | https://carsonk.net/
